Error: Error: The Pterodactyl Panel Shows An Error "Failed To Connect To MySQL: SQLSTATE[HY000] [2002] Connection Refused" When Attempting To Start A Minecraft Server.

Solution: 1. First, verify that your MySQL server is up and running.
